<indexterm zone="hb-directwrite-face-create" role="2.4.0"><primary>hb_directwrite_face_create</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C"><link linkend="hb-face-t"><returnvalue>hb_face_t</returnvalue></link>&#160;*
hb_directwrite_face_create (<parameter><link linkend="IDWriteFontFace"><type>IDWriteFontFace</type></link> *font_face</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>Constructs a new face object from the specified DirectWrite IDWriteFontFace.</para>
